Package: gander
Title: Context-rich LLM chats at the tooltip
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Couch", , "simon.couch@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5676-5107"))
Description: The package introduces a higher-performance and lower-friction 
    chat experience for data scientists. ellmer chats are integrated directly 
    into your RStudio and Positron sessions, automatically incorporating 
    relevant context such as surrounding lines of code, variable summaries 
    (like data frame columns and types), function documentation, and images. 
    After triggering the package addin, type your request and the assistant 
    will stream its response directly into your documents.
